-- Russia’s Mechel May Close One Romanian Unit, Money Channel Says
-- B y   A n d r a   T i m u
-- 2012-08-30T06:48:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-30/russia-s-mechel-may-close-one-romanian-unit-money-channel-says.html
OAO  Mechel (MTLR) , Russia’s largest
producer of coal for steelmakers, may shut down one of its
Romanian units beginning in September, private television
station  The Money Channel  reported, citing union members.  Mechel seeks to fire about 800 employees from its Campia
Turzii unit in the center of the country, a measure that could
be followed by a complete shutdown of the unit, according to The
Money Channel.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andra Timu in Bucharest at 
 atimu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
